App Indexing is now also used
as a ranking signal on Android

00:03:52.770 --> 00:03:56.240
to help provide users with
the most relevant and specific

00:03:56.240 --> 00:03:58.550
search results possible.

00:03:58.550 --> 00:04:00.860
Growing and keeping
users on your app

